caption: The ambiance was clean, comfy, and smell great. Besides, the waiter greeted me good morning in a nice manner and with a smile. Honestly, when I already have my order, I smiled because of the nice treatment. Also, when I already taste the coffee, I find it delicious and tasty. Eventually, I felt lively and energetic. Till next time!
